law.text:
This title does not apply to:
the abuse of a patient in a mental health facility, under Title 10 of the Health - General Article;
the abuse of a patient in a facility for individuals with an intellectual disability under Title 7 of the Health - General Article;
the abuse of a patient in a nursing home under Title 19 of the Health - General Article; or
the abuse of a patient in a hospital under Title 19 of the Health - General Article.
